playbookOutput.executionSummary:
Pigs in a blanket: A classic kid-pleaser! Wrap hot dogs in crescent roll dough and bake until golden brown. <https://noblepig.com/> 

Ants on a log: Celery sticks filled with peanut butter (check for allergies!) and dotted with raisins. <https://healthyhappylife.com/ants-on-a-log/> 
Chicken nuggets or tenders: They're a crowd favorite for a reason! Choose baked or grilled options for a healthier twist.<https://cookiesandcups.com/homemade-chicken-nuggets/> 
Chicken quesadillas: Fill tortillas with shredded chicken, cheese, and other toppings like beans or corn. Serve with salsa, guacamole, and sour cream for dipping. <https://www.melskitchencafe.com/the-best-chicken-quesadillas/>
